data.config.yaml:
apiVersion: config.kubestash.com/v1alpha1
kind: KubeStashConfig
certDir: /var/serving-cert
enableHTTP2: false
health:
  healthProbeBindAddress: :8081
metrics:
  bindAddress: 127.0.0.1:8443
  secureMetrics: true
webhook:
  port: 9443
leaderElection:
  leaderElect: false
  resourceName: cba9d7ad.kubestash.com
imagePullSecrets:
  []
webhookInfo:
  validating:
    enable: true
    name: kubestash-kubestash-operator
  mutating:
    enable: true
    name: kubestash-kubestash-operator
docker:
  registry: ghcr.io/anisurrahman75
  image: kubestash
  tag: fix-dep-bug_linux_amd64
netVolAccessor:
  cpu: 100m
  memory: 128Mi
  user: 0
  privilegedMode: true
networkPolicy: false
